=== Purchase Information === Product Title: AuroTrends Makeup Remover Towel,2 Pack Reusable Chemical-free Microfiber Makeup Remover Cloths,Magically and Gently Wipe Away Cosmetics,Sunscreen,Oil and Dirt,Set of 2 (Pink+Black) Review Date: 2019/01/08 Store: AuroTrends Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Brand': 'AuroTrends', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Material Feature': 'Reusable', 'Unit Count': '2.0 Count', 'Number of Items': '2', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '7.52 x 2.72 x 1.42 inches; 6.4 Ounces'} Review Text: These are really soft. Also, even when they are soaking wet, they don't feel drippy. I am weird about having water on/in my face, and these cloths allow me to wash my face without triggering an odd anxious feeling. I really like these cloths and always keep one on hand. Review Title: Really Soft Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: TELETIES - Spiral Hair Coils - Ponytail Holder Hair Ties for Women - Phone Cord Hair Ties - Strong Grip, No Rip, Water Resistant, No Crease Hair Tie Coils - 3 pack (Large, Maliblu) Review Date: 2020/07/23 Store: Teleties Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Material': 'Fabric', 'Item Form': 'Spiral', 'Brand': 'Teleties', 'Hair Type': 'Curly', 'Number of Pieces': '3', 'Package Dimensions': '3 x 3 x 1.2 inches; 2.08 Ounces', 'UPC': '711841892807'} Review Text: I love telephone cord style hair ties. They gather all of my hair into a ponytail or bun easily and, best of all, they don't give me headaches like more traditional hair elastics. These are a pretty combination of aqua blue and white, and they are very sturdy. Review Title: No Headaches Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: RAREKIND Fade Matte Lipstick by Amorepacific - 10 Colors, Cruelty-Free Nourishing Lip Stick, Velvety-smooth, Long-Lasting Moisturizing Lipstick - 3.2g Maple Road Review Date: 2020/09/03 Store: RAREKIND Average Rating: 3.8 Product Details: {'Package Dimensions': '3.3 x 0.9 x 0.9 inches; 0.95 Ounces'} Review Text: Eh. The color is bit more orange-y than I’d hoped for by the photo. It’s really thick. It doesn’t stay put or feel great on. I might try mixing it with some gloss if I liked the color more. Review Title: Not thrilled Rating: 2.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Reusable Cotton Swab Portable Silicone Swab Washable Cotton Swabs for Ear Cleaning Beauty Treatment Makeup Cotton Swab Review Date: 2020/09/25 Store: JAOYU Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Product Dimensions': '3.2 x 3.2 x 0.39 inches', 'UPC': '739232135913'} Review Text: I was skeptical. I am autistic, and I hate the feel of water in my ears, so I use cotton swabs to dry my ears after a shower. This adds up to a lot of swabs and I felt guilty about putting that many into the trash when I could make a tiny difference environmentally. I didn't really think the silicone option would work. The cotton soaks up the water. But the little knobby end actually does pull the water out of my ear canal.

The case is fine. I feel like the rubber bit that holds it together will eventually break. It is just flimsy. But, for now, it does its job. I ordered the blue, and it is a pretty dull blue, but the swab works, so whatever. Review Title: It Works Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: KISSIO Lipstick Set,4Pcs Cigarette Matte Lipstick Set,Red Matte Pigmentation Lipstick,Long Lasting Waterproof Lipstick for women Review Date: 2020/12/13 Store: KISSIO Average Rating: 4.3 Product Details: {'Brand': 'KISSIO', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Item Form': 'Stick', 'Finish Type': 'Matte', 'Product Benefits': 'Long Lasting,Cleansing,Moisturizing,Long-lasting,Makeup', 'Package Dimensions': '10.79 x 8.27 x 0.47 inches; 2.01 Ounces'} Review Text: These are fine. They don't stay very well though, and they make my lips a bit dry, so I still end up adding a lip balm over top, and that sort of ruins the matte finish. The color is good. I like the size of the container as well, like a lip balm. Review Title: Nice Colors Rating: 3.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Long Curly Wig for Women Black Long Wavy Wigs with Bangs Synthetic Replacement Wig Heat Resistant Natural Looking for Daily Party Cosplay (Black) Review Date: 2021/03/31 Store: GUDEMAY Average Rating: 2.9 Product Details: {'Material': 'Synthetic', 'Hair Type': 'Curly', 'Style': 'Modern', 'Special Feature': 'Glueless', 'Brand': 'GUDEMAY', 'Package Dimensions': '10.98 x 9.96 x 2.32 inches; 10.86 Ounces', 'UPC': '779880641428'} Review Text: [[VIDEOID:da59496c84540ec5e1ead467d50fa820]] I adore this wig.

So, it isn't black. It is brown. Or else, they accidentally sent me the brown version. Regardless, I love how it looks on. The hair doesn't have that super-shiny fake look of plastic. It falls nicely. I will post a photo. Review Title: Pretty! Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 2PCS Wine Red&Black mixed Brown 14''Short Curly Bob Wig with Air Bangs for Women Shoulder Length Wavy Wigs Synthetic Heat Resistant Fiber Hair Medium Length Glueless Wig for Daily Wear Review Date: 2021/06/15 Store: OSWINMART Average Rating: 3.7 Product Details: {'Material': 'Synthetic', 'Item Dimensions LxWxH': '14 x 9.5 x 8.5 inches', 'Hair Type': 'Curly', 'Special Feature': 'Glueless', 'Brand': 'OSWINMART', 'Product Dimensions': '14 x 9.5 x 8.5 inches; 1.08 Pounds', 'UPC': '732043538942'} Review Text: I like the darker one a lot. The lengths for both wigs are good, and the bangs work pretty well. Although I prefer the darker one, other people have commented that they like the reddish one better. So both work well and look good on. The darker one is super close to my real style on a good hair day, just with added bangs, so I am sure I will get a lot of use out of it. Review Title: Both are Great! Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: SHIONLE - Semi Matte Air Lipstick: Creamy semi matte lipstick | Long Lasting | Great Coverage | Creamy Texture | 06 CRUSH BERRY | 3.3g Review Date: 2021/07/18 Store: SHIONLE Average Rating: 3.4 Product Details: {'Brand': 'SHIONLE', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Item Form': 'Cream', 'Finish Type': 'Matte', 'Product Benefits': 'Long Lasting,Moisturizing', 'Product Dimensions': '1 x 3 x 1 inches; 0.12 Ounces'} Review Text: Slightly browner than expected, but it still is a color that works with my skin tone. It lasts as long as any lipstick, so not forever, but good enough. It doesn't feel too thick on my lips. Overall this one was a win. Review Title: A win Rating: 4.0 --------------------------------------------------

The individual exhibits a strong preference for high-quality, reusable beauty products, demonstrating a commitment to sustainability. Consistent positive sentiments are noted for items with soft textures and comfort, enhancing their experience, particularly in makeup removal and hair accessories that avoid causing discomfort. Common themes reveal a focus on makeup and hair solutions designed for everyday use, indicating practicality and ease of use as essential factors.

Quality is prioritized, but the individual is moderately price-sensitive, as seen in the mixed ratings for lip products, which often do not meet their expectations for longevity and feel. Personalized styling options like wigs are explored, reflecting a desire for versatility, though satisfaction levels are lower due to quality discrepancies. 

Overall, core preferences highlight a blend of functionality and comfort with an inclination towards eco-friendly choices, while maintaining a critical eye for product performance and value. target_interaction.text: I can see how these might work well in some hair types, but they aren't great for mine. My hair is very fine and tends to slip right out of these. The wires are also totally out of shape after one use and you can bend them back but they're never quite straight again.
